1441
01:30:09.457 --> 01:30:13.335
It was a form of tissue expansion
known as ballooning.

1442
01:30:15.713 --> 01:30:18.090
This procedure is often used on the scalp

1443
01:30:18.174 --> 01:30:20.550
Dr. Michael May FRCS - HAIR TRANSPLANT
SPECIALIST. THE WIMPOLE CLINIC

1444
01:30:20.635 --> 01:30:25.806
to treat burns. scarring.

1445
01:30:27.308 --> 01:30:29.309
This is done by the surgeon

1446
01:30:29.394 --> 01:30:34.940
inserting a plastic balloon underneath the skin

1447
01:30:35.024 --> 01:30:40.153
and. over a period of time.
increasing the volume of the balloon.

1448
01:30:40.988 --> 01:30:44.241
and therefore. stretching the skin above.

1449
01:30:47.036 --> 01:30:48.703
The surgeons.

1450
01:30:48.871 --> 01:30:50.622
almost like drawing a curtain.

1451
01:30:50.706 --> 01:30:55.168
bring the normal tissue over that area of scalp

1452
01:30:55.837 --> 01:30:58.839
and fill in the scarred area.

1453
01:31:02.343 --> 01:31:04.803
I actually spoke to Dr Steven Hoefflin.

1454
01:31:04.887 --> 01:31:09.558
who did the first ballooning procedure
on Michael after the Pepsi incident.

1455
01:31:09.684 --> 01:31:11.393
And he explained to me

1456
01:31:11.519 --> 01:31:16.106
Michael continued to do the ballooning procedure

1457
01:31:16.190 --> 01:31:19.025
