1458
01:31:19.861 --> 01:31:22.154
It was quite painful. you can imagine.

1459
01:31:22.238 --> 01:31:28.285
If a large balloon of saline
is placed beneath the skin.

1460
01:31:28.369 --> 01:31:32.414
