1629
01:42:12.179 --> 01:42:14.472
He was hurt. He was really hurt.

1630
01:42:14.681 --> 01:42:19.602
La Toya Jackson and her husband.
boyfriend. I guess. at that time. Jack Gordon.

1631
01:42:19.686 --> 01:42:23.648
and I went to Spain to do a TV show together.

